		name : "Psychic Shield",
			name : "Psychic Shield",
			source : [["wotPE", 131], ["X", 35]],
			minlevel : 3,
			description : desc([
				"At 3rd level, you become wreathed in a semi-luminous, magical aura. You shed a psychic aura in a 10-foot radius, that makes everyone uncomfortable.",
